## 2026-03-29 - Extract shared buildTokenDiff helper and fix unsafe git status parsing
- Extracted `buildTokenDiff(fileDiffs)` helper in `sync.ts` to replace 4 identical flatten→compare→diff blocks (~55 lines each → 1 function call each)
